name: Them's the Brakes
description: Little big red rum and coke reminds me of a killing joke. A muscle car on muscle beach, just picked up a Georgia peach. That's when things got kinda fuzzy. Radio, static, eerie, buzzy. Middle of the road just standing there. A gray alien, in underwear. It's far too late. Now way past heavy. Cut to the chase. Watch out! The Chevy! No one saw that coming, I'll bet. Least of all the Red Corvette.
